---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - JamBuddy" description="Learn about the story behind JamBuddy and our mission to enhance musical creativity and collaboration.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-20 rounded-lg">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">About JamBuddy</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        A stripped-down tool for beginners chasing the chords in the tunes that haunt them.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-900 rounded-lg">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">My Story</h2>
          <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-300">
            <p class="mb-6">
              I'm Steve Ewing, the lone outlaw behind JamBuddy. I picked up a uke last year, tumbled headlong into the guitar soon after, and needed a tool to sniff out the chords that kept slipping through my fingers.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-6">
              I'm a data scientist by trade, but app development was uncharted territory. JamBuddy is my first ride into mobile apps—wrangling audio with machine learning while learning the ropes of Android.
            </p>
            <p>
              This app is my fix for a real problem: something that listens to whatever music's blaring and spits out the chords so beginners like me can finally keep up.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-purple-500/20">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-indigo-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19V6l12-3v13M9 19c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zm12-3c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zM9 10l12-3"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">My Goal</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              Make learning an instrument less of a slog by letting folks spot the chords fast and get back to playing.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- App Principles -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-900/80 rounded-lg mt-8">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">App Principles</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          The creed I follow while building this unruly thing
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Beginner Friendly</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            Built for newcomers chasing chords without slogging through years of ear training.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Simple & Useful</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            No bloated gimmicks—just sharp chord detection for any tune that crosses your path.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Constantly Improving</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            I'm learning as I go, both in code and music. The app toughens up as my skills do—your feedback fuels the next round.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About the Developer -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-900 rounded-lg mt-8">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">About the Developer</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Independent developer blending data science with a love for music
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-12">
        <div class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/20 max-w-2xl">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center text-left">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-600 to-gray-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">SE</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Steve Ewing</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-medium mb-4">Data Scientist & Music Enthusiast</p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 mb-3">
                I'm a data scientist and indie developer. After learning ukulele and guitar, I created JamBuddy to help musicians identify chords quickly.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300">
                My focus is applying machine learning to audio analysis. When I'm not coding, I'm researching new techniques to improve JamBuddy.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- App Features -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-900 text-white rounded-lg mt-8">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">What JamBuddy Can Do</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">
          Straightforward features that keep your learning on track when the music gets rowdy
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-center">
        <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-700">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-700 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15.536 8.464a5 5 0 010 7.072m2.828-9.9a9 9 0 010 12.728M5.586 15H4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h1.586l4.707-4.707C10.923 3.663 12 4.109 12 5v14c0 .891-1.077 1.337-1.707.707L5.586 15z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Chord Detection</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            Uses your phone's mic to sniff out chords from any source, be it your own picking or a dusty recording
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-700">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-700 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Wear OS App</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            A watch companion that flashes the chord changes so your hands never leave the strings
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-700">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-700 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19V6l12-3v13M9 19c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zm12-3c0 1.105-1.343 2-3 2s-3-.895-3-2 1.343-2 3-2 3 .895 3 2zM9 10l12-3"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Multiple Instruments</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            Handles guitar, ukulele, mandolin, and baritone uke with the right diagrams for each
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-700">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gray-700 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Jam Song Collection</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300">
            A stash of old-time and bluegrass standards with progressions to guide your picking
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-black/80 rounded-lg mt-8">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Join Open Testing</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        JamBuddy is still taking shape. Grab the open test on Google Play and holler back with your thoughts.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jambuddy" class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors flex items-center">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M17.9,2.4c-0.1,0-0.2,0-0.2,0l-11,5l-3.8-3.8c-0.3-0.3-0.8-0.3-1.1,0s-0.3,0.8,0,1.1l3.2,3.2l-3.2,3.2 c-0.3,0.3-0.3,0.8,0,1.1c0.2,0.2,0.4,0.2,0.6,0.2c0.2,0,0.4-0.1,0.6-0.2l3.8-3.8l11,5c0.1,0,0.2,0.1,0.2,0.1c0.2,0,0.3-0.1,0.5-0.2 c0.2-0.2,0.3-0.4,0.3-0.7V3.3C18.8,2.8,18.4,2.4,17.9,2.4z"/>
          </svg>
          Download on Google Play
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors flex items-center">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
          </svg>
          Send Feedback
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>